the salt card is designed to end the tiresome task of manually unlocking a smartphone or tablet by automatically making it come to life whenever the user is nearby . the credit card-sized gadget also locks devices again as soon as a user moves out of range at a distance of 10 feet -lrb- three metres -rrb- . it connects to an app on a user 's android handset or iphone via bluetooth and also tells them if they have strayed too far from their wallet
