the image was created by superimposing a blurry picture of albert einstein . features with a high spatial frequency -lrb- einstein -rrb- are only visible from further away . combining pictures of the two produces a single image which changes when the viewer moves closer or farther away from the screen . this classic optical illusion was created several years ago by neuroscientists at the massachusetts institute of technology .
