the ring , located 12 billion light years away , is an illusion created by the chance alignment of two distant galaxies . the striking circular structure is a rare manifestation of gravitational lensing predicted by albert einstein in his theory of general relativity . the bright orange central region of the ring reveals the glowing dust in this distant galaxy .
